cs.AR, cs.AI, cs.ET, cs.SY, cs.DC

This paper is about hardware acceleration of neural network inference on FPGAs, which falls under the intersection of computer architecture (cs.AR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses energy efficiency (cs.ET) and system-level design (cs.SY), as well as the use of Boolean logic (cs.DC) in FPGA implementations.
